---
title: Spicy Prawn and Chorizo Pasta With Chargrilled Courgettes
description: We love Prawn Pasta With Chargrilled Courgettes and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-prawn-pasta-spicy-prawn-and-chorizo-pasta-6d4cb3dd-9bb51f4c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spicy-prawn-pasta-spicy-prawn-and-chorizo-pasta-6023a412d59e21649b2a0dcb-c54a1adb.pdf
